ong\u2011distance flights**. Candidate\u202fB is the only one with explicit, unequivocal evidence of both (100\u202f% reliability and calmness in crisis). While his interpersonal style is a concern, the other candidates either lack proven reliability/responsibility or have significant teamwork and communication deficits that could directly affect flight safety.\nTherefore, I consider Candidate\u202fB the strongest overall fit for the long\u2011distance pilot position.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
